{"type":"message","id":"396a23ae","parentId":"2dff70f9","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:25:04.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I should also check what \"Capability Evolver\" was about and why it was running. But the main thing is HALEI is frustrated that I keep forgetting things despite MEMORY.md existing. The issue is:\n\n1. I loaded MEMORY.md but didn't check for newly added entries like the uninstalled Capability Evolver\n2. I don't check MEMORY.md thoroughly enough before taking action\n3. I don't update MEMORY.md proactively when important decisions are made\n\nLet me also note that the learnings directory was missing, which contributed to not having a proper place to log this error. But more importantly, I should write a note about the pattern of forgetting things.\n","thinkingSignature":"70720638c9b28ba5c6f20a7a089b033a851c0c8d581aba7f896712d15ba9905d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ahvzv2uz3y58_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# LEARNINGS.md - 教训和发现\n\n## 纠正\n\n### 2026-05-17：总是忘记已卸载的功能\n\n**问题：** 反复触发 Capability Evolver 更新，但该功能早已卸载。\n\n**根本原因：** \n- 我确实读取了 MEMORY.md，但只读不写——配置变更后没有立即更新 MEMORY.md\n- 没有在 MEMORY.md 中建立\"已卸载功能\"的明确列表\n- learnings/ 目录之前不存在，说明更早的教训也没有被系统性地记录\n\n**纠正措施：**\n1. 配置变更后立即更新 MEMORY.md（不能拖到\"以后\"）\n2. 已卸载/禁用的功能要在 MEMORY.md 开头建明确清单\n3. 建立 learnings/ 目录，每次犯错都要写下来\n4. 触发自动化任务前先查 MEMORY.md 中对应功能的安装状态\n\n**教训：** 记忆文件不是摆设——读了不够，要写，要维护。上下文恢复时优先读 MEMORY.md 的\"已卸载/禁用\"清单再行动。\n\n## 知识盲区\n\n（暂无）\n\n## 最佳实践\n\n（暂无）","path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/learnings/LEARNINGS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1324,"output":420,"cacheRead":27549,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779024282294,"responseId":"0658f49ad281a56240341d0ba7654186"}}
